## Description {#details}

Sort a LocationT-&gt;SampleT map by LocationT.

It produces a sorted list of &lt;LocationT, SampleT&gt; records by ascending order of LocationT.

Definition at line 1353 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/profiledata/sampleprof-h">SampleProf.h</a>.
